Fields in com.orchestranetworks.service declared as ImportSpecMode
static ImportSpecMode ImportSpecMode.INSERT
          Insert mode: only record creations are allowed.
static ImportSpecMode ImportSpecMode.REPLACE
          Replace (synchronization) mode: if a record with the same primary key exists in the target table, it is updated, otherwise, a new record is inserted; if a record is not present in the source, it is deleted.
static ImportSpecMode ImportSpecMode.UPDATE
          Update mode: only modifications of existing records are allowed.
static ImportSpecMode ImportSpecMode.UPDATE_OR_INSERT
          Update or insert mode: both record creations and modifications of existing records are allowed.
